## Features
- **Per-player KeepInventory**
- **Nickname & Skin changer**
- **Anti-Armour-Breaking**
- **Server Freeze**
  - Complete server lockdown: blocks movement, commands, interactions, inventory access, dropping items, mining, and placing blocks
  - Optional: **Skin API Server Freeze** (halts external skin lookups during freeze)
- **Accelerated HP regeneration** + **2× food effectiveness**
- **Everything configurable** via commands and config file

## Commands
/unstablesmp nick <player> <nickname>      — Set another player's nickname  
/unstablesmp skin <player> <skinName>      — Change another player's skin  
/unstablesmp resetnick <player>            — Reset a player's nickname  
/unstablesmp resetskin <player>            — Reset a player's skin  
/unstablesmp randomnick <player>           — Assign a random nickname  
/unstablesmp randomskin <player>           — Assign a random skin

## Configuration
- All features togglable and configurable in a single config file (per-world and per-group overrides recommended).  
- Commands provide runtime control and parity with config values.

## Notes
- Persist nickname and skin changes across restarts.  
- Gate nickname/skin commands by permission nodes.  
- Design server-freeze to optionally disable external skin API calls for stability.
